lead_paragraph: Japan's Mika Miyazato got off to a red-hot start on Thursday on the way to a seven-way share of the lead after a drama-filled opening round in the season-opening Pure Silk-Bahamas LPGA Classic at Paradise Island.

headline.print_headline: Miyazato in Seven-Way Tie for Lead in the Bahamas
